{"tid":1244112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"伊利沙伯醫院急症室護士 啱啱睇左HA secret","createTime":"2019-06-19T18:05:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T05:39:05.000Z","uid":237145,"like":69,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f2283d5f15151bc24342af997afa94028a82f8a7","tid":1244112,"uid":237145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:05:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/731331330322257/posts/2188227261299316/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F731331330322257%2Fposts%2F2188227261299316%2F&d=ZVysXiw7s3azMdswkJgtbBTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=52c6f31d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/731331330322257/posts/2188227261299316/</a><br />\n<br />\nHA secret 又爆料<br />\n<br />\n正正係伊利沙伯醫院急症室嘅醜聞<br />\n<br />\n大家一定覺得<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">護士肯撚定係狗係垃圾</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地聽到都好震驚<br />\n雖然冇fact check 但諗個個都會信左先 包括我地<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>當日唔係現場 唔洗你問我答</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n開post 係好想同大家講 如果係真嘅話<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我地都好撚嬲點解會有呢啲敗類係我地身邊！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n重申一句<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">伊利沙伯醫院急症室有好多正直熱血嘅醫護</span></span><br />\n懇求大家唔好因為啲<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>個别例子</strong></span></span>污名化我地<br />\n<br />\n雖然我地只可以代表自己<br />\n但係都好想同全港市民講句<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果件事係真嘅 <strong>對唔住</strong></span></span><br />\n身為佢地嘅一分子 我地覺得好羞恥<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點解要迫我地成為你地嘅其中一員</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望市民大眾唔好唔信醫院<br />\n好嘅醫護人員一定比唔好嘅多<br />\n有急事一定要嚟<br />\n唔好因為政治原因諱疾忌醫<br />\n<br />\n我地依然堅信<br />\n香港肯定仲有一班有良心嘅醫護為市民服務<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>求下大家唔好係護士都屌 好大壓力㗎</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">如果係假嘅 咪當粉筆字抹左佢囉</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88511411625c342462f74c9dd42b0aa64948c618","tid":1244112,"uid":114186,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:06:46.000Z","msg":"對唔住無用 叫多啲人21號出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa604e0d9947fdca3dbdb510da9d792626754286","tid":1244112,"uid":241504,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:06:52.000Z","msg":"護士都割<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8338581861db5d795b618b2e787ba6579bc43a0c","tid":1244112,"uid":237145,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"88511411625c342462f74c9dd42b0aa64948c618","tid":1244112,"uid":114186,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:06:46.000Z","msg":"對唔住無用 叫多啲人21號出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:10:30.000Z","msg":"梗係會出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到時見"},{"pid":"16b588a6daac59709332dfab092cec38364cf579","tid":1244112,"uid":237145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aa604e0d9947fdca3dbdb510da9d792626754286","tid":1244112,"uid":241504,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:06:52.000Z","msg":"護士都割<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:10:48.000Z","msg":"如果係你會點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d270