 class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ffe363f64efa5cb511d98e1eb64fc7cb6b2a806","tid":1244112,"uid":213728,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:32:32.000Z","msg":"分流站個金毛女護士好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲叫我小心d"},{"pid":"472d72220ae391c91b5d69e9a3c149985c79a564","tid":1244112,"uid":119283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:35:01.000Z","msg":"用番大陸嗰招<br />\n佢分化，<br />\n你篤灰。<br />\n抽條二五出嚟。<br />\n再要叫哂所有得閒嘅人621 行出嚟作投名狀。<br />\n咁樣我諗全部人會信你地並且保護你地。"},{"pid":"4d57df8b815d4e3cf6c2eb342aee5b279d95153f","tid":1244112,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:48:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/78MsPpy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F78MsPpy.png&h=88e6213a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CAa1TRf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCAa1TRf.png&h=d52c7487&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ywt64XW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fywt64XW.png&h=bb7f8a38&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ze4RwCY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fze4RwCY.png&h=8db99c05&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"162f87f7d53ecc313cee6d384e3ac830296f41be","tid":1244112,"uid":181549,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:15:04.000Z","msg":"呀dom成日落黎數人頭<br />\n叫我地返工唔撚好講政治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申612發夢有出<br />\n<br />\n同香港人站同一陣線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />釋放義士！"},{"pid":"ec3558b0070994615cf39fa83ec84866a86bacf1","tid":1244112,"uid":65556,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T04:17:35.000Z","msg":"相信你<br />\n懇請前線醫護人員要盡一切能力去保住我地任何一位義士"},{"pid":"90a08c7ee9331db5bcc432cefba2f08228e807ec","tid":1244112,"uid":198822,"like":0,"di